---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Disclaimer | TendersMW"
  description="TendersMW disclaimer — important information about our tender aggregation service."
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text mb-6">Disclaimer</h1>
    <div class="glass-card p-6 space-y-4 text-sm text-muted">
      <p>TendersMW is an independent tender aggregation platform. We are <strong class="text-text">not affiliated with</strong> the Public Procurement and Disposal of Assets Authority (PPDA), the Government of Malawi, the World Bank, African Development Bank, European Union, United Nations, or any other organization whose tenders we list.</p>

      <p>The information on this website is collected from publicly available sources and is provided for informational purposes only. While we make every effort to ensure the accuracy and timeliness of tender listings, we cannot guarantee that all information is complete, accurate, or current.</p>

      <p><strong class="text-text">Before submitting any bid or proposal:</strong></p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li>Verify all tender details directly with the procuring entity</li>
        <li>Download official tender documents from the original source</li>
        <li>Confirm closing dates and submission requirements</li>
        <li>Ensure you meet all eligibility criteria</li>
      </ul>

      <p>TendersMW accepts no responsibility for any loss, damage, or expense arising from the use of information on this site or any actions taken based on such information.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
